title: Hitachi HNAS: System Drives
agents: hitachi_hnas_rest
catalog: hw/storagehw/hitachi
license: GPLv2
distribution: Kuhn & Rueß GmbH
description:
 This check monitors the system drives (LUNs) of a Hitachi NAS
 (HNAS) system via the File Storage REST API. It requires the
 special agent "Hitachi HNAS via REST API" to be configured for
 the host.

 The service is OK if the system drive status is OK, otherwise it
 goes CRIT. A degraded drive is also reported as CRIT, and a drive
 whose access is not allowed as WARN.

item:
 The ID of the system drive.

discovery:
 One service is created for each system drive.
